headline: DOGE's Potential Impact - Top 10 IT And Software Companies With Exposure To The U.S. Government
summary: While it's unclear how enforceable DOGE suggestions will be, we used Syntax Data's Functional Information System to identify IT services/software companies most susceptible to spending cuts.
